1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
The most powerful sorcerers

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:05,000
in history are hollow.

3
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,500
My sister lies dying,

4
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:12,000
on the cold stone floor.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,500
One spell can mend her.

6
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:19,500
The ancient text demands sacrifice.

7
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:23,500
I must burn every memory,

8
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:27,500
to fuel the light.

9
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,500
I raise my hands.

10
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:34,500
Her image blurs to static.

11
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:37,000
I save her,

12
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:40,000
but I walk home,

13
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,600
a stranger to her now.